05-05-2016
- Added possibility to fetch of multiple nodes via comma separator.
  e.g.: ...&node=8,9,34
- Added search suggestions. Ability to define search string and field where
  search is to be made. Also support for regular expressions in 'query' parameter.
  e.g.: ...&query=ding_*&field=type
        ...&query=ding_page&field=type
        ...&query=^alpha&field=fields.title.value

